    <div class="col-2 sidebar">
        <div class="sidebar-top"></div>
        

<div class="side-img pull-quote">
    <div class="blockquote-container">
        <p class="blockquote">On December 31, 2010, the low tax rates on capital gains and<br/>dividends enacted in 2003 will increase to the higher level that<br/>applied prior to that year. Many economists agree that the<br/>expiration of these tax cuts will discourage investment and slow<br/>economic growth. The United States already has one of the world's<br/>highest capital gains tax rates.</p>
    </div>
</div>

