							<div class="two-column-even about">
								<h5>ABOUT <em class="georgia">The</em> HERITAGE FOUNDATION </h5>
								<div class="col-1">
                                    
		<p>The Heritage Foundation is the nations most broadly supported public policy research institute, with nearly 700,000 individual, foundation and corporate donors. Heritage, founded in February 1973, has a staff of 255 and an annual expense budget of $75.3 million.</p>
    <p>Our mission is toformulate and promote conservative public policies based on the principles of free enterprise, limited government, individual freedom, traditional American values, and a strong national defense. <a title="About The Heritage Foundation" href="/about/">Read More</a></p>
								</div>						
								<div class="col-2">
